{"tid":1557673,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"韓國瑜：不是我想選總統 是人民選我出來 讓我當候選人","createTime":"2019-09-10T08:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T16:29:42.000Z","uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cf4eeb7d09212a865818c60832aed537eaa23d06","tid":1557673,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:12:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2909814\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2909814&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdDyPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=d24cebb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2909814&h=f8d12845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2909814</a><br />\n<br />\n即時新聞／綜合報導〕高雄市長韓國瑜今（8）日在新北三重造勢，韓的國政顧問團長張善政在現場向韓粉們指出，不是韓國瑜想選總統，「是你跟我期待他出來」，「是我們拱韓國瑜出來選」，替韓表達原本無心選總統之意。<br />\n張善政今現身韓國瑜造勢晚會批評民進黨政府，張說：「這幾年台灣百業蕭條，餐飲業、百貨業說蔡英文再當選，他們都要打包了」，張也批評蔡政府提出的前瞻計畫中，所包含的離岸風電、太陽光電技術「不成熟」，要韓粉支持國民黨重啟核四政策。"},{"pid":"ed07f039411c27baa9f82b488e5b1d118e7484ec","tid":1557673,"uid":25468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/34187.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F34187.jpg&h=19186a7a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50268ac913108dffb0299b3c96d1683ee3fe8e13","tid":1557673,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:15:47.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data